{"command":"run","hypothesis":"修复参数接线后，对 r289 做单变量校正：shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert 的最终重构可写为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r1(x))} γ_{e,j} b_{e,j}，其中 h(x) 是 low-rank scorer、r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh。共享库与 expert 子库都是静态向量库，在线侧仍是查表 + 加权求和 + residual cleanup，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。r289 的高 cost 主要来自继承了 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256；本轮只把该值改回 56，测试低秩 shared scorer 回到 matched-cost 带后，这个 family 是否还能换回更低 exceed。","summary":"已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 的 override allowlist，使 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 不再被 runtime 拦截。基于 `reference_round=289` 仅改一个 env 参数：`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=56`。本地自检已确认解析链路只改这一项，且 smoke 通过；该配置的本地 cost 估计回到 `selection≈0.07x, deploy≈0.04x, total≈0.11x`，避免继续把 r289 的 `0.257x` 高 cost 误判成结构本身失败。","change_type":"edit_perf_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"这轮不是继续细扫 recipe，而是修正 r289 的变量隔离失效：上一轮 architecture probe 继承了不匹配的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`，导致 cost 证据失真。风险是即便 cost 回到 0.11x 左右，exceed 仍可能没有竞争力；若如此，应把该 family 在当前 hookpoint 上降级，而不是继续追加 low-rank shared 线性跟参。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"56"}],"touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘修复 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`：为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 增加 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `STAGE1_RATIO` / expert-layout 相关 allowlist，解除该 family 的 env override 拦截。","本地校验通过：`validate_env_overrides([FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=56], fallback_architecture=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert) == []`。","本地解析链路通过：以 `reference_round=289` 解析后，`changed_keys == ['FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM']`，reference 配置中的 `256` 已正确覆写为 `56`。","本地 smoke 通过：`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 在 `K=32, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=56, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：`selection_ratio≈0.07, deployment_ratio≈0