_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.09，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.13；处于当前允许的 matched-objective 探索带。","该 family 的结构语义是：dual shared residual coarse stage 吃主干，PK experts 做中层 cleanup，tiny factorized residual head 做尾部 cleanup；与 r294 相比，信息增量集中在 hard-token tail-cleanup 机制。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r294 且 objective 改善，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次极小幅 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO`。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则说明在 dual-shared PK scaffold 上追加 tiny global residual cleanup 的交换率不足，后续应停止继续叠加同类 cleanup 层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先按 exact architecture string 回查 config whitelist / dispatch / class reachable 性，而不要把问题误判成训练质量结论。"],"reference_round":294}
